All right, so what are some of the highlights

00:25:53.599 --> 00:25:55.680
from the manuscripts?

00:25:55.680 --> 00:25:58.439
We can see that we have multiple formats

00:25:58.439 --> 00:26:00.520
from a single source.

00:26:00.520 --> 00:26:05.520
So all of our narrative is in that index.qmd file,

00:26:05.599 --> 00:26:10.599
but by stating multiple out formats in our Quarto YAML,

00:26:11.439 --> 00:26:16.319
I'm able to get a Word, a PDF, and a Mecha bundle as well.

00:26:16.319 --> 00:26:18.719
So let's go back up here

00:26:18.719 --> 00:26:22.560
and see if I can actually click on this MS Word file.

00:26:22.560 --> 00:26:24.839
You can see that I downloaded it.

00:26:26.160 --> 00:26:29.959
I think I actually need to, give me one second.

