I'm going to go ahead and share my full screen now.

00:26:38.319 --> 00:26:43.319
So this is the Word file that I was able to sort of create.

00:26:43.439 --> 00:26:46.959
And you can see the contents are basically the same,

00:26:46.959 --> 00:26:49.160
even though it looks a lot different.

00:26:49.160 --> 00:26:53.680
And similarly, if we take a look at the PDF file here,

00:26:53.680 --> 00:26:56.760
this is formatted particularly for PLoS.

00:26:57.680 --> 00:27:01.000
And so you can see that PDF file here as well,

00:27:01.000 --> 00:27:03.359
and we can download the Mecha bundle too.

00:27:04.599 --> 00:27:07.719
All right, go ahead and do this.

00:27:07.719 --> 00:27:10.760
So in addition, in order to get to this,

00:27:10.760 --> 00:27:14.599
this is what our Quarto YAML file looked like.

00:27:14.599 --> 00:27:19.599
I have, as you can see, four outputs that are listed.

