to using the journal extension for PLoS.

00:28:00.520 --> 00:28:03.760
And you can also see that I have an option

00:28:03.760 --> 00:28:07.560
to keep the tech file, the intermediary tech file,

00:28:07.560 --> 00:28:11.719
which I find especially helpful as I work on a manuscript.

00:28:11.719 --> 00:28:14.640
Every once in a while, there are some tech errors

